{"tid":1891551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲賣「 銀離子洗手凝露」，又俾個上次插佢話「SARS唔使醫」嗰個醫生追擊","createTime":"2020-02-22T02:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T18:44:23.000Z","uid":271829,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a3e1bb97af255b747848bbb6cec330d35e250763","tid":1891551,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nexn1hf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNexn1hf.jpg&h=9aaa5656&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TbpqeCg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTbpqeCg.jpg&h=14afcad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n信徒用完請分享下<br />\n銀質沈著症的症狀為皮膚呈現藍灰色（一種只影響外觀的皮膚變色症狀），這是因為人體內的銀含量過高。在學者Gaul和Staud的43個銀質沈著症案例中，銀質沈著症有（63%）是由醫藥上使用的銀膠（Collargol或Argyrol）所引起，其他則是由碘化銀或氯化銀所引起的。銀的毒性雖然很低，但很高的濃度下會得到銀質沈著症以外的人體毒性（老鼠的半致死口服劑量為1600mg/kg/d）。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hans/%E9%8A%80%E8%B3%AA%E6%B2%88%E8%91%97%E7%97%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hans%2F%25E9%258A%2580%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E6%25B2%2588%25E8%2591%2597%25E7%2597%2587&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAIgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=6f1a1cbe\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hans/%E9%8A%80%E8%B3%AA%E6%B2%88%E8%91%97%E7%97%87</a><br />\n___________________<br />\n//【銀離子同其他重金屬及其離子其實有毒，係可以殺死「細菌」嘅】但係消滅「病毒」就未有太多文獻資料。而食咗「銀」產品，就可以「預防病毒」？分分鐘濃度高到自己中毒死咗，都未完全消滅病毒。到今日為止只係發現到銀嘅納米粒子，有可能對抗到病毒，但係詳細都未證實。//<br />\n@k kwong ,<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/%E4%B8%80%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%B8-%E9%8A%80%E9%9B%A2%E5%AD%90%E6%AE%BA%E6%AF%92/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%25AD%25B8-%25E9%258A%2580%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%25AF%2592%2F&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAIgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=67feb7a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%25AD%25B8-%25E9%258A%2580%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%25AF%2592%2F&h=5821917a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/%E4%B8%80%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%B8-%E9%8A%80%E9%9B%A2%E5%AD%90%E6%AE%BA%E6%AF%92/</a><br />\n___________________<br />\n《Journal of Electroanalytical Chemistry》<br />\n&quot;Characterization of Ag+ toxicity on living fibroblast cells by the ferrocenemethanol and oxygen response with the scanning electrochemical microscope&quot;<br />\n<br />\n► Silver ion was toxic to fibroblast cells and Ag(0)-containing clusters were formed.<br />\n___________________<br />\n<br />\n#銀離子<br />\n#定銀紙嚟<br />\nIG. EyeSuperSuperUK<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/eyesupersuperuk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Feyesupersuperuk&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAIgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=563597fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/eyesupersuperuk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2087023804867501/posts/2595046927398517/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2087023804867501%2Fposts%2F2595046927398517%2F&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAIgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=300b42e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2087023804867501/posts/2595046927398517/</a>"},{"pid":"0af4d5bd102be3530b4739549e412d4d5abd0382","tid":1891551,"uid":271199,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:32:37.000Z","msg":"anyway 相信青山雲伯都係on9"},{"pid":"de1f6696916d7e780dcfb103ef1b0ce479987626","tid":1891551,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:50:43.000Z","msg":"救救醫護，工會做野，醫護集體大移民<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fckKuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fckKuS</a>"},{"pid":"60a6f4448764fd